cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.CL

This paper deals with error correction codes, which are commonly used in communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also uses machine learning concepts such as node embedding and self-attention, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper deals with graph permutation selection, which could place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
